      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade vehicle in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen has been curated for the discerning collector, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in an untouched state. Subjected to a rigorous multi-point technical evaluation, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, offering uncompromising performance and aesthetic perfection. Detailed documentation of its fastidious maintenance history is available for review.",
      "price": 43900.0,
