    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve truly babied this ride, and it shows in every single detail. If you\u2019re looking for a dream car that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next big adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
