      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powerplant with its signature eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip M-differential. The chassis remains rigid with zero subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides perfect articulation across all drive modes. Preventative maintenance is complete, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Novillo leather shows no bolster wear. Strictly garage-kept and never tracked. Pre-purchase inspections at specialized shops are welcomed.",
